001A34  1               
001A34  1               ;******************************************************************
001A34  1               ; Shield sprite pixel data — 16x16 4bpp, 128 bytes each
001A34  1               ;
001A34  1               ;   Color 0 = transparent, Color 7 = dark green (palette entry 7,
001A34  1               ;   set to dark green by init_shields).
001A34  1               ;   Each byte encodes 2 pixels: high nibble = left, low nibble = right.
001A34  1               ;
001A34  1               ;   Damage progression: each level erodes 4 more rows from the top,
001A34  1               ;   replacing solid color-7 pixels with a 2-pixel checkerboard of
001A34  1               ;   color 7 and transparent.  Rows not yet eroded remain solid.
001A34  1               ;
001A34  1               ;   Checker A (odd bits lit):  $70 $07 $70 $07 $70 $07 $70 $07
001A34  1               ;   Checker B (even bits lit): $07 $70 $07 $70 $07 $70 $07 $70
001A34  1               ;   Solid row:                 $77 $77 $77 $77 $77 $77 $77 $77
001A34  1               ;
001A34  1               ;   Classic Space Invaders arch/bunker shape (16x16, 4bpp, color index 7)
001A34  1               ;   Dome on top narrows upward; arch notch cut from bottom center.
001A34  1               ;   Damage progression: dome erodes from top, arch widens from bottom.
001A34  1               ;
001A34  1               ;   shield_tile_full:  intact bunker
001A34  1               ;   shield_tile_dmg1:  dome top shrunk + two holes, arch 1 row deeper
001A34  1               ;   shield_tile_dmg2:  dome mostly gone, arch very wide, bottom gone
001A34  1               ;   shield_tile_dmg3:  only side pillars remain, dome gone
001A34  1               ;******************************************************************
001A34  1               
